name: Mind is the limit of achievement
description: we are what we think, everything about us arises with our thoughts, through our thoughts create the world, in the universe of thoughts there are interesting patterns of our thoughts, when we think of lofty goals, then naturally your mind and body will adjust, initiative emerges and creativity is accelerated. This painting conveys a message and the motivation behind it implies a struggle between strength and weakness, hope and despair. with the encouragement of the mind there is hope for the growth of new ideals and futures, self-improvement for the better.
